snippet.title: New Style Boutique 2 - Fashion Forward - Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Nintendo presents: New Style Boutique 2 - Fashion Forward comes to Nintendo 3DS on 20th November.

You can give New Style Boutique 2 a try right now with a free demo available on Nintendo eShop!

Official Website: http://newstyleboutique2.nintendo.co.uk
Facebook New Style Boutique: https://facebook.com/NewStyleBoutiqueUK
Instagram Nintendo Girls Club UK: https://www.instagram.com/NintendoGirlsClubUK/
